Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好担心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为戈薇再也不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不好好的跟戈薇道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人是怎么搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  八成是\N戈薇姑娘愿意妥协吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许犬夜叉和桔梗劈腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可置信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇居然能忍受这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为犬夜叉太会钻牛角尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在穷追猛打我想不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他从平常就没从容过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他也有点不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第49话  琥珀失去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是奈落的城的遗迹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留着些许奈落的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连点痕迹都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的有座城才是怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是  现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也是把我们\N诱骗到假的城里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时看到的城是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落之城的确曾经在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  找到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家父的铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候  我们这些驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被诱骗到奈落城里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  家父与同伴惨遭杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下手的人  是我的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子受奈落所操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸首就埋在庭院的一角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让令尊与大家的遗骨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弃置在这种不祥之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把他们\N带到适当的地点好好供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说这里就是奈落的城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城中的那些人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚那\N受奈落所控制的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会也跟着城堡一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会被野狗挖出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时就请各位安眠于此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在我们的村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的为各位造墓的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然村子里已经没有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还有我与琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人可以守着坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是琥珀他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙子  手艺真不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的看得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还让你帮忙砍柴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到屋里喝点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  有想起什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是自己从哪来之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最起码该知道自己的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在这个城附近的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概十天前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人见大人的城仿佛失踪般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天就发现你倒在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是经历什么很可怕的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会什么都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系  别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对对  在你想起来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢怎样都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  还有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量多吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我似乎曾在那里待过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公公  老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以千万不要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们这段时间的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从城里逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天  城消失的晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没有活下去的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你父亲跟同伴的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫…琥珀?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有四魂碎片的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近了  就在森林那一带
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的目的也是四魂碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  把埋在你体内的\N四魂之玉碎片交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把碎片交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那妖怪想夺走\N琥珀体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的性命全靠\N埋在体内的四魂碎片维系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片一旦被取出…他就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被奈落控制了心智…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在奈落的城里才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手腕受伤了  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我以前见过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从城里逃走前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奈落也不记得?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没有活下去的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你父亲跟同伴的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  那就是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子一定是在演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看起来不像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  以前出现在\N我们面前的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛被抽走魂魄的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们两人独处不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为珊瑚说想和他独处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔师的村落?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我们以前住在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我也能驱逐妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见习的程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下  待会还得工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你也准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经十一岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也差不多该参与实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪真的会吐出火或毒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们驱除的\N通常只是大蛇或大蜘蛛之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最可怕的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些伪装成人形的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到四魂之玉的话就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  被奈落叫去的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好是琥珀第一次上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你所知的  请全部告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛昔日的琥珀般…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖巧而有点胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点慢慢的回想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今后我们会一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不太好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是姐弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从奈落的手里逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扁他两三拳不就现出原形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这么简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管这是不是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昔日最疼爱的弟弟已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是陷阱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚会大受打击的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为奈落\N最喜欢玩弄人的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都不说的话  我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等不要这样子  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…关于琥珀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奈落的陷阱不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是想要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我除了相信还能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奈落的技俩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不是我们及时赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片被抽出来话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟就会真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  这就是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好像因为\N自己在这里的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而害那个温柔的人遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是太疼弟弟才分不清道理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆  你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好给我认清现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且本来就是犬夜叉你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是一大群
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的手下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们难道是针对琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片的气息移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要保护琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐  你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们将琥珀藏起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想装蒜  他是奈落养的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀那家伙竟然趁乱逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片还在他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是来带他回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落也真是小题大作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过想要四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就带这么庞大的阵仗来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说目标是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  不过没了那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀就会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体就丢给他姐姐珊瑚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么追来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的目标是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  不要再离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要对我这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我唯一的亲弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  琥珀交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去阻止它们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲到那个洞里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在犬夜叉他们来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  珊瑚很强的  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你还没想起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚是你姐姐的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚被迫和你分开后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间一直很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她平常很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有时也会露出落寞的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以琥珀回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以和她在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话\N你就能想起她的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能想起那个人的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么可怕的东西\N我非想起来不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了她  杀了戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破魔之矢用光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:12.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:19.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:27.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:35.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆被消除的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然受奈落的操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实行奈落命令杀害戈薇的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚知道这件事情之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:24:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定杀了琥珀然后再自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现是陷阱而拼命的\N消灭毒虫与妖怪的弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉快一点
